15:05.654 --> 15:08.657
And, uh, just lately,
I've been feeling a little overwhelmed.

15:13.954 --> 15:16.123
-Oh! I love Rush.

15:16.206 --> 15:19.293
-Did you play this for me?
-Uh… I'm not sure.

15:19.376 --> 15:20.836
