15:20.920 --> 15:22.338
Cool with me. Everybody poops.

15:22.421 --> 15:24.340
-No, thank you.
-Thanks for this!

15:28.594 --> 15:29.970
I think it's a flute.

15:35.142 --> 15:36.018
Oh!

15:42.441 --> 15:44.151
Oh, come on! What ha--

15:44.234 --> 15:45.986
-What--
-No, Frisbee, get out.

15:46.070 --> 15:49.531
-You made the music turn off. Get out!
-I… just wanted to see what the fun was.

15:49.615 --> 15:50.658
All right.

15:54.703 --> 15:55.788
Tom?

15:55.871 --> 15:57.414
I need some privacy, please.

15:57.498 --> 15:59.750
Oh, no, Clark.
It's me. God.

16:00.250 --> 16:01.293
Oh, my gosh.

16:01.377 --> 16:02.878
You're not gonna faint.

16:02.962 --> 16:05.089
Come on out
