16:07.383 --> 16:08.509
Your pants are still up.

16:10.219 --> 16:11.053
Okay.

16:14.306 --> 16:15.182
Hi.

16:15.975 --> 16:17.601
Um…

16:18.727 --> 16:21.397
And fo… for the record, I guess
I always figured you--

16:21.480 --> 16:22.564
you would be a woman.

16:22.648 --> 16:26.568
