where we won't get murdered by Satan.

22:03.447 --> 22:05.157
-Yeah.
-Get in the back, Clark.

22:05.240 --> 22:07.701
-Oh God! What? What's going on?
-I know. Let's go!

22:09.036 --> 22:10.912
-I'm here to save your bacon, bud.
-Oh.

22:10.996 --> 22:12.331
-What is happening?

22:12.414 --> 22:14.082
-Oh!] Whoa!

22:14.166 --> 22:16.501
-Oh, shit! Go, go, go, go!
-Satan is happening.

22:16.585 --> 22:18.253
Did you miss me?

22:22.382 --> 22:24.760
-Go! Come on, man!

22:27.888 --> 22:30.432
-Shit.
-Why is my car so slow?

22:30.515 --> 22:32.851
I don't mean
to throw anyone under the bus,

22:32.934 --> 22:35.479
but Frisbee was supposed
to Harry Potter the car.

22:35.562 --> 22:38.398
Fucking Frisbee!
If he would do some work once in a while

22:38.482 --> 22:40.442
instead of doing paperwork
about doing work,

22:40.525 --> 22:42.527
-we'd all be in better shape!
-Tell me about it.

22:45.989 --> 22:48.617
-Did you talk to the reporter?
-She was on a date.

22:48.700 --> 22:51.411
-I'm supposed to talk to her tomorrow.
-God's not gonna like that.

22:52.120 --> 22:54.289
-Shit.

