-You know, whatever.

25:11.843 --> 25:12.886
Okay, well.

25:14.763 --> 25:17.098
Is that something
you'd like to make official?

25:17.182 --> 25:20.101
Yes, I would. Yes. If…
But did I answer too quickly?

25:20.185 --> 25:22.354
'Cause I-- I can, like, give it a beat.

25:22.437 --> 25:26.525
Uh… but-- but it's not,
like, a pressure thing.

25:26.608 --> 25:30.904
It just was something that was brought up
today in kind of an unusual situation.

25:30.987 --> 25:32.197
